article_title: SNP MP condemns 'man-made catastrophe' of Gaza war.
sentence: The  SNP's  Chris  Law  says  he  is  just  back  from  Cairo  where  aid  workers  told  him  of  a  "man-made  humanitarian  catastrophe"  -    tens  of  thousands  of  innocent  people  killed,  horrific  injuries,  and  Gazans  with  "nowhere  to  go".
